    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains a reliable driver, the exterior shows visible signs of age including several door dings, faded paint on the roof, and a small crack in the rear bumper. The interior has some wear on the upholstery and the air conditioning is currently blowing cool but not cold. It has been regularly serviced, but a buyer should expect to invest in some minor cosmetic and mechanical maintenance soon. It is a solid, functional car for anyone looking for affordable transportation.",
