    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a second lease on life and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to get their hands dirty. While it definitely needs some mechanical attention and significant TLC to get back to its prime, it\u2019s a budget-friendly way to start your next automotive adventure and build something you're proud of!",
